</div>
</div>
<h3>A+ Tier — The Best of the Best</h3>
<p>These sonic fan games are excellent. Each one brings something unique to the table, and any of them could easily be someone's personal favorite.</p>
<div class="tier-s-card">
<h4><a href="/sonic-gt/">Sonic GT</a> <span class="tier-a-badge">A+ TIER</span></h4>
<p>Built on a custom engine called Bumper Engine, Sonic GT delivers momentum-driven 3D platforming across 4 full zones with boss fights. Seven playable characters — including unlockable Classic Sonic and Metal Sonic — explore massive levels packed with alternate routes and a Chaos Emerald hunting system. One of the most complete fan games currently available, and it keeps getting bigger with every update.</p>
<div class="tier-s-previews">
<a href="/wp-content/uploads/2026/sonic-gt/coastal-zone-full.webp" data-lightbox><img src="/wp-content/uploads/2026/sonic-gt/coastal-zone-thumb.webp" alt="Sonic GT - Ocean Paradise coastal zone" loading="lazy" /></a>
