</div>
<div class="tier-s-card">
<h4><a href="/sonic-before-the-sequel/">Before the Sequel</a> <span class="tier-a-badge">A+ TIER</span></h4>
<p>Bridges Sonic 1 and Sonic 2 narratively with an iconic original soundtrack that rivals the best in the franchise. Originally created by LakeFeperd in 2011 — the developer who went on to create Spark the Electric Jester — this rebuilt 2026 version by Usumily features updated sprites, near-Genesis-accurate controls, and the same legendary music. You can feel the talent in every level.</p>
