<div class="tier-s-card">
<h4><a href="/sonic-p-06/">Sonic P-06</a> <span class="tier-a-badge">A+ TIER</span></h4>
<p>A ground-up reconstruction of Sonic 2006 in Unity by solo developer ChaosX. Nine playable characters — Sonic, Shadow, Silver, Tails, Knuckles, Rouge, Omega, Blaze, and Amy — across three full campaigns with rebuilt controls, reworked physics, and visuals that surpass the original. Available on PC and Android. This is the Sonic Adventure 3 that never was.</p>
