<div class="tier-s-card">
<h4><a href="/smackdown/">Sonic Smackdown</a> <span class="tier-a-badge">A+ TIER</span></h4>
<p>Built in Unreal Engine, Sonic Smackdown is a legitimate competitive fighting game with unique movesets per character, 1v1, 2v2, and 3v3 tag modes, and rollback netcode for online play. The Ultimate version features cel-shaded 3D models, DBFZ-inspired mechanics, and full controller support including fightsticks. This is not a novelty — it stands on its own merits alongside Street Fighter and Guilty Gear.</p>
