<h4><a href="/sonic-and-the-fallen-star/">Sonic and the Fallen Star</a> <span class="tier-a-badge">A+ TIER</span></h4>
<p>A complete 2D adventure spanning 9 full zones with Sonic and Tails playable, special stages, and animated cutscenes between every zone. What sets it apart is its entirely original art direction — custom sprites, hand-crafted palettes, and a dual original soundtrack by Holly Taylor. Features a unique "Nova Sonic" super transformation. One of the most visually distinct classic-style fan games ever made.</p>
