<p>Built in Unreal Engine on the Velocity Plus framework by developer Novazaru, Sonic Daybreak fuses classic momentum physics with Modern Sonic speed and Adventure-style exploration. Features one of the largest movesets in any Sonic game, commercial-quality visuals, multi-path stages with Red Rings, and an S-rank system. Reviewers gave it a straight 10 out of 10.</p>
